message: Register THREE global for UMD build
Only build ESM version for dev mode
Export package.json for Svelte and others :)
Remove empty dependencies entry from package.json

Replace serve with live-server

Provides live reloading in yarn dev's web server.

Use EventEmitter for tick events

Also, a cool new example! (match-three.html)

Merge branch 'release'
